description: Foodies of Ellicott City just love eating Tigi’s Ethiopian cuisine, and it’s now it’s even extra exciting that Tigi’s is taking their incredible food to events all around town. Chef Tigi & his wife Bellete truly believe in cooking with the highest quality ingredients and serving their food with the utmost care. Because of this, Tigi’s Ethiopian Restaurant quickly became a local favorite. Folks just rave about all the tasty food from their menu, which includes delicious vegan and meat dishes alike, including the Duba Wot (savory pumpkin stew, flavored with garlic, spices, and barbere’) or the Yebeg Tibs (luscious cubed lamb, sauteed in spices, onion, garlic, ginger, and butter), and so much more. All the guests at your next event are sure to love Tigi’s delightful variety of delectable authentic cuisine. For a mouthwatering meal made with passion and talent, you simply must try the food from Tigi’s.
name: Tigi's Ethiopian Restaurant & Market
